original_title: LES CHIENS NE FONT PAS DES CHATS
overview: Pregnant and homeless, Joëlle shows up at her father’s house. Even if Jeff, a solitary non-conformist former punk is reluctant to the idea, Joëlle decides to stay. Jeff is overwhelmed by the casualness of his daughter, whom he barely knows.
title: DOGS DON'T BREED CATS
